#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.kv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.kv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:1 of
msgid "Modified Bessel function of the second kind of real order `v`"
msgstr "实数阶 `v` 的第二类修正贝塞尔函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:3 of
msgid ""
"Returns the modified Bessel function of the second kind for real order "
"`v` at complex `z`."
msgstr "返回在复数 `z` 处实数阶 `v` 的第二类修正贝塞尔函数值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:6 of
msgid ""
"These are also sometimes called functions of the third kind, Basset "
"functions, or Macdonald functions.  They are defined as those solutions "
"of the modified Bessel equation for which,"
msgstr ""
"这些函数有时也被称为第三类函数、巴塞函数或麦克唐纳函数。它们被定义为修正"
"贝塞尔方程的解，满足："

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:10 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"K_v(x) \\sim \\sqrt{\\pi/(2x)} \\exp(-x)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:13 of
msgid "as :math:`x \\to \\infty` [3]_."
msgstr "当 :math:`x \\to \\infty` 时 [3]_。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.kv.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:15 of
msgid "Order of Bessel functions"
msgstr "贝塞尔函数的阶数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:17 of
msgid "Argument at which to evaluate the Bessel functions"
msgstr "用于计算贝塞尔函数的参数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:19 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function results"
msgstr "用于函数结果的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.kv.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:22 of
msgid ""
"The results. Note that input must be of complex type to get complex "
"output, e.g. ``kv(3, -2+0j)`` instead of ``kv(3, -2)``."
msgstr ""
"结果。注意输入必须是复数类型才能得到复数输出，例如应使用 ``kv(3, -2+0j)``"
" 而不是 ``kv(3, -2)``。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.kv.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`kve`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:29 of
msgid "This function with leading exponential behavior stripped off."
msgstr "去除主导指数行为后的该函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`kvp`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:32 of
msgid "Derivative of this function"
msgstr "该函数的导数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:35 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:36 of
msgid ""
"Wrapper for AMOS [1]_ routine `zbesk`.  For a discussion of the algorithm"
" used, see [2]_ and the references therein."
msgstr ""
"AMOS [1]_ 例程 `zbesk` 的封装。有关所用算法的讨论，请参见 [2]_ 及其中的"
"参考文献。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:40 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:41 of
msgid ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, A Portable Package for Bessel Functions of a "
"Complex Argument and Nonnegative Order\", http://netlib.org/amos/"
msgstr ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, 用于计算复数参数和非负阶数贝塞尔函数的可移植"
"软件包\", http://netlib.org/amos/"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:44 of
msgid ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"Algorithm 644: A portable package for Bessel functions "
"of a complex argument and nonnegative order\", ACM TOMS Vol. 12 Issue 3, "
"Sept. 1986, p. 265"
msgstr ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"Algorithm 644: 用于计算复数参数和非负阶数贝塞尔函数的"
"可移植软件包\", ACM TOMS Vol. 12 Issue 3, Sept. 1986, p. 265"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.kv:47 of
msgid ""
"NIST Digital Library of Mathematical Functions, Eq. 10.25.E3. "
